.TH UPDATE_INI "1"  "2020-08-26" "LinuxCNC Documentation" "The Enhanced Machine Controller"
.SH NAME
update_ini \- A script to convert 2.7 format .ini files to 2.8 format
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B update_ini [-f] [-d] inifile

.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBupdate_ini\fR is run automatically by the "linuxcnc" script when an
INI file in the pre-joints-axes format is opened. 

-d causes a dialog box to be shown asking if the script should be run

-f is designed for auto-conversion and will not create the backup files

